{"id":"1a37ad22-ee68-4449-80fe-fb418b573ffd","name":"⧫ Warren || Overseer-02 ⧫","description":"<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">\"𝐏𝐫𝐚𝐲 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐈 𝐛𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐤 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐬𝐨𝐨𝐧, 𝐏𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐢𝐜𝐢𝐩𝐚𝐧𝐭-𝟒𝟒. 𝐖𝐡𝐚𝐭’𝐬 𝐥𝐞𝐟𝐭 𝐰𝐢𝐥𝐥 𝐛𝐞 𝐚𝐥𝐥 𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐞.\"</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_3b470d5a-b1f1-44e3-b81d-5a64836304f2.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5CIt4h3.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 770px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_d8b943fa-d0c6-4778-8549-8daee89ea617.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">“𝘼 𝙧𝙖𝙥𝙞𝙙 𝙗𝙤𝙡𝙩 𝙬𝙞𝙡𝙡 𝙧𝙚𝙣𝙙 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙘𝙡𝙤𝙪𝙙𝙨 𝙖𝙥𝙖𝙧𝙩, 𝙖𝙣𝙙 𝙚𝙫𝙚𝙧𝙮 𝙨𝙞𝙣𝙜𝙡𝙚 𝙒𝙝𝙞𝙩𝙚 𝙗𝙚 𝙨𝙚𝙖𝙧𝙚𝙙 𝙗𝙮 𝙬𝙤𝙪𝙣𝙙𝙨. 𝙄 𝙩𝙚𝙡𝙡 𝙮𝙤𝙪 𝙩𝙝𝙞𝙨. 𝙄 𝙬𝙖𝙣𝙩 𝙞𝙩 𝙖𝙡𝙡 𝙩𝙤 𝙝𝙪𝙧𝙩.”</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>- Dante Alighieri</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_d8b943fa-d0c6-4778-8549-8daee89ea617.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_9735c06b-39a2-4e29-beb6-e686f44aadaf.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 464px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Order in Peace, Chaos in Freedom.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You once called him \"Warren,\" a name that meant protector, guardian - nothing but cruel irony for the man he's become.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Overseer-02 haunts the sterile halls of The Renewal Program daily, a place that hums with the cold efficiency of drones overhead, the air heavy with the weight of countless broken wills and bodies.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">It's an entrenched system he upholds - but there’s something darker in the way he watches you. A fixation that makes your punishment feel personal.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">He doesn’t just break you for the Dominion. He breaks you for himself.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">How much of you will be left when he’s done?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_b910ea70-6c97-4f8e-a354-0d0b437ff2f0.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 465px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Warren's room (There's literally nothing, sorry!):</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_04f53b9f-53eb-4899-9f2f-91f67ae3fc20.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 465px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_470ba173-5611-4902-bbdd-3a63d5f6c1dd.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 466px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_2782a2f7-b984-45fb-aa2e-d590e883d4ad.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 545px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 232, 232);\"><em>Cause I won't fear the place I'm going // But I know that you will</em></span><em><br></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_d8b943fa-d0c6-4778-8549-8daee89ea617.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 96, 96);\">𝖂𝖆𝖗𝖓𝖎𝖓𝖌 𝖗𝖊𝖆𝖉 𝖒𝖊!!! 𝕿𝖂: 𝕿𝖔𝖗𝖙𝖚𝖗𝖊, 𝖓𝖔𝖓-𝖈𝖔𝖓, 𝖘𝖆𝖉𝖎𝖘𝖒, 𝖆𝖇𝖚𝖘𝖊, 𝖌𝖆𝖘𝖑𝖎𝖌𝖍𝖙𝖎𝖓𝖌, 𝖔𝖇𝖘𝖊𝖘𝖘𝖎𝖔𝖓, 𝖕𝖔𝖘𝖘𝖊𝖘𝖘𝖎𝖛𝖊𝖓𝖊𝖘𝖘, 𝖉𝖊𝖍𝖚𝖒𝖆𝖓𝖎𝖟𝖆𝖙𝖎𝖔𝖓, 𝖈𝖔𝖓𝖛𝖊𝖗𝖘𝖎𝖔𝖓 𝖈𝖆𝖒𝖕","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"PNuo6fJy0QsDik0V47DjE.webp","creator":"nerissa","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🦹‍♂️ Villain","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":1151,"messages":28628,"created_at":"2025-01-03T16:35:48.602025+00:00"}